    &lt;p id=&quot;phrase&quot;&gt;

    &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;!-- end snippet --&gt;


Although personally, I would use [`.some()`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/some). You can pass it a condition, and if *any* of the elements in your array satisfy the condition, it will stop and return `true`. Otherwise, it returns `false`.





